						               													<description>The Haunted House: Raon is a word game using Korean alphabet, Hangul, tiles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to Play:&amp;#10;(1) Make a face-down deck with a boss card and ten ghost cards.&amp;#10;(2) Place the Hangul tiles face-up in the center of the table.&amp;#10;(3) Open the top card from the deck.&amp;#10;(Each card tells you what kind of words to make)&amp;#10;ex: a word start with &amp;lsquo;&amp;not;&amp;rsquo; or &amp;lsquo; &amp;rsquo;, a word related to &amp;lsquo;plants&amp;rsquo;&amp;#10;(4) Use the tiles in the center to make words under a given condition.&amp;#10;(5) Players get points depend on the order they finish.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The biggest difference from the original Raon game is that there are now ghost cards to defeat!&amp;#10;The ghosts and the bosses can be defeated by making specific types of words written on each card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
